Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.22,0:00:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}柑菜她
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.96,0:00:10.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喜歡你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.17,0:00:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}谷川她對我…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.93,0:00:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.33,0:00:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你這是…谷川讓你說的？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.29,0:00:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不 是我自己的獨斷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.30,0:00:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}谷川同學她…對海人…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.68,0:00:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\an8}Music pick up 這次的嘉賓是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.71,0:00:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\an8}即將舉辦演唱會，越發出名的…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.82,0:00:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人他…打算如何呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.33,0:00:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.96,0:00:45.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這並不是谷川同學直接對他表白
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.61,0:00:48.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}大概也只會一如往常吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.09,0:00:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}石垣同學為什麼要對海人說…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.64,0:01:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 累死了累死了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.15,0:01:02.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}咦 你在家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.86,0:01:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真是的 又在做這種不上進的事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.70,0:01:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你家那隻又和智叔吵架了？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.51,0:01:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.35,0:01:13.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}本來打算和高中時候的朋友去旅行的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.40,0:01:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}結果大家突然就有事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.04,0:01:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}難得我回來一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.15,0:01:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.71,0:01:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼了？這麼沒精神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.57,0:01:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}和柑菜吵架了？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.48,0:01:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為什麼會提到柑菜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.31,0:01:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你幹什麼…！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.04,0:01:38.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}給你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.16,0:01:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}和大家一起好好享受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.72,0:01:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沖繩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.11,0:03:15.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒~沖繩？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.26,0:03:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}後天去？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.29,0:03:18.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}免費？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.34,0:03:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}當然要去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.89,0:03:21.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}如果說是和大家一起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.22,0:03:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}爸爸媽媽應該也會同意的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.92,0:03:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}檸檬學姐那邊就由我來聯繫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.80,0:03:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你能和美櫻還有海說一聲不
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.36,0:03:32.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}可…可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.94,0:03:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好機會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.76,0:03:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}別…別說了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.41,0:03:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我不是說了別提那件事嗎 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.28,0:03:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}先這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.13,0:03:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喂 這裡是霧島家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.05,0:03:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}谷…谷川
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.44,0:03:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎…怎麼了 這麼晚打來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.59,0:04:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}谷川同學打來的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.80,0:04:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}旅遊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.65,0:04:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}去沖繩？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.61,0:04:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什麼啊 原來是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.75,0:04:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.44,0:04:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就那樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.37,0:04:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}拜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.05,0:04:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}剛才的電話是谷川同學那邊打來的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.56,0:04:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.90,0:04:18.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}邀請我去旅遊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.34,0:04:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要去嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.32,0:04:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我是想去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.36,0:04:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這麼簡單就！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.11,0:04:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}學姐接下來有什麼安排嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.53,0:04:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}說是包括拍攝電影 要大家一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.71,0:04:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊…這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.87,0:04:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要去的是 沖繩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.29,0:04:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.13,0:04:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沖繩？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.21,0:04:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這…這就是沖繩？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.75,0:04:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}居然能得到這麼漂亮地方的應答
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.75,0:04:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\fscx50\fscy50\pos(915,664)}reply
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.74,0:04:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}應…答？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.49,0:04:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}唔…雖然不太明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.89,0:04:53.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你喜歡那嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.88,0:04:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}非常！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.88,0:04:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要去嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.56,0:04:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}絕對要去！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.75,0:05:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那 什麼時候去呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.95,0:05:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不知道該怎麼說好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.89,0:05:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那時的我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.73,0:05:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}其實真鬆了一口氣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.31,0:05:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不用去想什麼複雜的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.39,0:05:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}只要和大家一起享受旅行就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.20,0:05:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這麼想著
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.27,0:05:29.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}來了呢 沖繩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.95,0:05:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.40,0:05:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}來了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.37,0:05:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 要來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.57,0:05:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在說什麼要來了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.22,0:05:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎…怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.76,0:05:46.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒 只是覺得你還真是下了心思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.59,0:05:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}才…才不是那樣啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.41,0:05:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}只是店員和我說這個很流行就推薦給我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.01,0:05:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是這樣的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.40,0:05:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}美櫻！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.45,0:05:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對不起…我亂講的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.93,0:05:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}騙人的 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.41,0:05:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}有什麼 挺配你的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.43,0:06:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.36,0:06:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.30,0:06:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}謝謝…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.84,0:06:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊…沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.58,0:06:11.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}美櫻穿的是什麼樣的泳衣？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.96,0:06:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒…沒什麼 就普通的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.39,0:06:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是我皮膚比較敏感
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.48,0:06:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以不能把風衣脫掉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.23,0:06:20.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}可惜了這麼好的身材
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.78,0:06:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不要一直看啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.66,0:06:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}然後…學姐她們呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.76,0:06:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.61,0:06:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.66,0:06:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在換衣服那花了點時間
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.93,0:06:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}久等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.03,0:06:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}來了真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.31,0:06:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}石垣同學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.68,0:06:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我穿得如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.58,0:06:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對於某些特殊人群效果拔群
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.45,0:06:47.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}能侵略陸地嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.22,0:06:48.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.91,0:06:50.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這樣是不是有點太成熟了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.21,0:06:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}抱歉…姐姐的泳裝都這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.12,0:06:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不會 很感謝你借給我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.63,0:06:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}虧我還…做好心理準備了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.66,0:07:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}Don't mind！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.18,0:07:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這還真是…毫無意義的鉅作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.08,0:07:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這才開始這才開始
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.88,0:07:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這才開始？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.84,0:07:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}也來埋埋海人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.34,0:07:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不了 我就算了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.20,0:07:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是嗎…？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.30,0:07:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}霧島同學 是不是有點怪怪的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.00,0:07:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\blur5}明明這麼好玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.67,0:07:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}也許吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.95,0:08:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}話說 現在開始是指？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.92,0:08:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}馬上就要漲潮了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.83,0:08:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}然後就看起來會像真的城堡一樣浮在水面哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.78,0:08:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}請求緊急撤離
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.20,0:08:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海 救救我！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.34,0:08:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那麼 沖繩的海也享受夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.85,0:08:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要開始拍攝了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.57,0:08:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.59,0:08:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}第一天就要？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.26,0:08:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}劇情我已經推敲好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.46,0:08:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為了逃脫緊逼而來的追兵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.73,0:08:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}女主角只好暫到沖繩藏身
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.07,0:08:29.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這劇情真的有經過推敲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.83,0:08:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}推敲過度結果都熬夜了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.97,0:08:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}肌膚 如水潤般光滑哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.95,0:08:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}總覺得 我們備受注目啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.05,0:08:48.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那是因為 你太美了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.29,0:08:49.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}呃 我不是說這個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.51,0:08:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不用徵得拍攝許可什麼的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.44,0:08:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}谷川同學 大海並不屬於誰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.14,0:08:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}後果自負哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.94,0:09:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個 請問你們在幹什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.11,0:09:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哦 那個…在拍個人電影
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.73,0:09:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒 好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.37,0:09:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}佳織 不能打擾人家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.14,0:09:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我只是問問而已嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.41,0:09:12.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 誒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.39,0:09:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}難不成是…小海？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.89,0:09:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你為什麼會知道我的小名
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.21,0:09:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}果然 是我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.49,0:09:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我啦 佳織
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.55,0:09:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}樹下佳織
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.43,0:09:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}樹下…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.87,0:09:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.99,0:09:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}樹下 真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.08,0:09:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.12,0:09:31.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好棒 好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.11,0:09:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}有多少年沒見面了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.39,0:09:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是我馬上就認出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.04,0:09:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}因為你完全沒變嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.49,0:09:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那頭卷髮和那副大眼鏡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.44,0:09:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}樹下 你倒是…變了很多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.69,0:09:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.85,0:09:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}上高中以後
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.96,0:09:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}女人味有所增加嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.24,0:09:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是 沒想到能在這種地方見到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.73,0:09:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真是太巧了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.75,0:09:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.29,0:09:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}霧島同學 這位是？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.37,0:10:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是我小學時候的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.03,0:10:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}未婚妻哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.62,0:10:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\pos(550,712)}未
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.30,0:10:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\pos(642,712)}婚妻？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.83,0:10:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那可真是喜聞樂見的關係啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.92,0:10:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.04,0:10:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}小時候流行像情侶配對那樣的遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.76,0:10:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那時我們是同桌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.33,0:10:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以班裡那些人擅自把我們配對了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.02,0:10:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真冷淡吶 人家當時可是很認真的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.58,0:10:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.39,0:10:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}畢業典禮的時候我不是還寫了情書給你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.04,0:10:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}有這回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.87,0:10:27.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真厲害啊 竟然能和初戀重逢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.21,0:10:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}果然吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.90,0:10:29.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}而且還是在沖繩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.17,0:10:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這就是命運啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.71,0:10:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 沒那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.60,0:10:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\an9}修羅場……
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.94,0:10:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真行啊 海老師
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.98,0:10:46.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個 請問貴姓
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.24,0:10:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 我叫石垣哲朗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.89,0:10:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}石垣先生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.08,0:10:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}請問您有女朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.10,0:10:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.97,0:10:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不 沒有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.41,0:10:57.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.63,0:11:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}小女子名叫有澤千春
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.94,0:11:01.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}差不多該放手了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.45,0:11:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.70,0:11:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}大家的表情都很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.93,0:11:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好棒的房子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.32,0:11:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}伙食也很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.23,0:11:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}燒烤什麼的我還是第一次呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.62,0:11:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是這樣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.58,0:11:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真的 能來沖繩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.14,0:11:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真是太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.43,0:11:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.85,0:11:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}說…說的是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.16,0:11:34.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}而且能與小學同學的命運般的邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.57,0:11:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真是個活潑又可愛的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.46,0:11:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}與連婚約都許下了的初戀情人再會
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.36,0:11:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真是一段良緣佳話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.50,0:11:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個…不是初戀哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.62,0:11:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我和那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.22,0:11:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.87,0:11:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}都叫人家「那傢伙」了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.54,0:11:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}轉眼兩人的關係就一如當初了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.52,0:11:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不 我和樹下真的什麼都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.31,0:12:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}話說 我為什麼會這樣被審問？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.13,0:12:04.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那是因為 貴月學姐被七海姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.42,0:12:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}「拜託了」要好好照顧海人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.41,0:12:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為了防止你被在旅途中才遇上的女生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.61,0:12:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}迷得神魂顛倒展開冒險的戀愛而已！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.81,0:12:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}都是為了不讓你這樣失足！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.87,0:12:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我才不會！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.97,0:12:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誰知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.15,0:12:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}拜託了 聽我解釋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.46,0:12:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}想找藉口啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.34,0:12:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不是啦 我只是想說明實情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.31,0:12:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海那傢伙也不容易啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.29,0:12:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哲朗…你又如何呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.21,0:12:29.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.39,0:12:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個叫有澤的女生 很可愛哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.77,0:12:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}身材也挺好的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.83,0:12:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}還交換了地址
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.18,0:12:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}可愛女生的請求 我可是來者不拒的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.46,0:12:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.71,0:12:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.76,0:12:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.43,0:12:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}介紹一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.94,0:12:56.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這是將要出演我們電影的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.26,0:12:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}樹下佳織同學
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.17,0:12:59.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.15,0:13:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}檸檬 你這是鬧哪樣啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.23,0:13:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沖繩篇需要友情客串
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.85,0:13:07.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}她能答應得這麼爽快真是幫大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.99,0:13:11.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我感覺好像有幾分「造作」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.40,0:13:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}她與我的構想正相配
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.89,0:13:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那不就是故意的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.43,0:13:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你在幹什麼 小海？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.28,0:13:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這是什麼懲罰遊戲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.77,0:13:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒有 這是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.72,0:13:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那麼 哪個才是小海的戀人？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.17,0:13:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不是…不是那樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.11,0:13:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哦 這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.52,0:13:31.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那麼我參與拍攝也沒問題咯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.53,0:13:34.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}小海你是導演吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.25,0:13:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要拍怎麼樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.81,0:13:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}果然沖繩還是要泳裝嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.01,0:13:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}說的是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.28,0:13:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不是的 我什麼都沒說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.21,0:13:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什麼都
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.37,0:13:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哲朗大人是24號出生的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.15,0:13:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那麼生辰食物是蘋果 生辰動物是天鵝 守護神是雅典娜吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.06,0:13:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}有著冷靜沉著的性格
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.32,0:13:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}雖然看起來要比真實年齡成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.98,0:13:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但其實是個情感十分纖細的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.78,0:13:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要說理想的對象的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.24,0:13:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是那種能強拉你一把的大膽開朗的女性為佳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.80,0:13:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}簡直就像是我們啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.78,0:14:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這兩位女生真夠厲害的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.64,0:14:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.32,0:14:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是樹下那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.86,0:14:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}以前不是那樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.63,0:14:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}而且還說要出演電影什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.57,0:14:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真讓人期待啊 明天的拍攝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.84,0:14:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你這是在耍我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.96,0:14:18.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.41,0:14:18.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.88,0:14:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.73,0:14:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.21,0:14:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好像有些累了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.23,0:14:33.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.11,0:14:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}態度總那麼曖昧…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.29,0:14:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}讓他說清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.89,0:14:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.30,0:14:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.78,0:14:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我…我在想什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.08,0:14:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這種事怎麼想也沒結果嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.30,0:14:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}因為
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.41,0:14:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.69,0:14:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.21,0:15:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我是？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.22,0:15:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}檸檬 什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.70,0:15:05.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我是聞到了香味
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.05,0:15:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}能給我來一杯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.98,0:15:10.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯…稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.90,0:15:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個 要加砂糖嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.61,0:15:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不需要 但要多加牛奶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.00,0:15:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}吶 一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.99,0:15:21.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}雖然那些孩子們也差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.27,0:15:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是你還是稍微坦率一點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.48,0:15:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.47,0:15:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}入境隨俗嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.97,0:15:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你…究竟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.25,0:15:36.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哎呀 我是指隨沖繩的俗哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.82,0:15:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這個也不好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.26,0:15:45.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}還沒決定好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.28,0:15:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}總覺得都沒有…讓人眼前一亮的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.70,0:15:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真是好可愛啊…柑菜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.56,0:15:59.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哈…？你是什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.19,0:15:59.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}等…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.51,0:16:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.19,0:16:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}又要這樣睡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.36,0:16:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我不這樣…就睡不好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.55,0:16:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你知道的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.59,0:16:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}把他還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.85,0:16:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.05,0:16:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}只要你乖乖束手就擒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.28,0:16:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你…你是什麼人？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.64,0:16:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你在這顆未經開發的星球上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.10,0:16:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}暴露了自己的真實身份
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.32,0:16:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}據聯邦法規定
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.24,0:16:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我要逮捕你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.06,0:16:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}銀…銀河警察的特工？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.10,0:16:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是又如何
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.16,0:16:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}CUT
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.01,0:16:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}呀 演戲真是好難呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.67,0:16:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好了啦 鬆手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.53,0:16:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不要害羞嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.41,0:16:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這樣太熱了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.60,0:16:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要是不熱我就能黏你咯？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.82,0:16:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不是那樣！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.98,0:16:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}又害羞啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.80,0:16:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真拿你沒辦法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.87,0:16:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.30,0:16:59.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}檸檬 還要拍多久呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.92,0:17:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\blur5}是呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.60,0:17:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\blur5}還有五六個景吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.95,0:17:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\blur5}這…這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.67,0:17:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}美櫻？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.84,0:17:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}攝影好有趣啊 哲朗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.75,0:17:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是…是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.06,0:17:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我對這個超感興趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.38,0:17:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}檸檬學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.13,0:17:17.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我把小道具忘在小屋裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.73,0:17:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}能去拿一下嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.24,0:17:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}快去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.44,0:17:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}了解
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.73,0:17:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哲朗…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.27,0:17:27.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真意外啊 我還以為他會色迷迷到底呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.64,0:17:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}因為感情很纖細啊 哲朗他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.15,0:17:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}纖細？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.51,0:17:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哲朗他？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.86,0:17:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.81,0:17:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}因為你離他太近了才沒注意到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.18,0:17:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.19,0:17:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.70,0:17:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人和樹下同學呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.14,0:17:50.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}小隻的那個也不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.56,0:17:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.03,0:17:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}難道是？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.99,0:17:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就是那個「難道」啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.52,0:17:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.28,0:18:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}然後 樹下你為什麼帶我來這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.16,0:18:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你明白的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.52,0:18:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}因為想要兩個人獨處啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.96,0:18:15.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嫌我煩了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.75,0:18:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}有什麼事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.91,0:18:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}雖然我不太明白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.40,0:18:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但你情緒這麼高有些怪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.32,0:18:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}因為和小海見面所以就有點高興過頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.44,0:18:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你這習慣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.34,0:18:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.32,0:18:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}小時候要是遇上什麼事或者有什麼不順
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.16,0:18:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就會這樣咬手指的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.92,0:18:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}有什麼事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.79,0:18:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以才會非要…那個…和我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.18,0:18:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}如果你不介意的話 就說給我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.33,0:18:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}如果是認真的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.76,0:18:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要是我是認真的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.98,0:18:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.32,0:18:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在哪兒呢 在哪兒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.20,0:19:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}其實沒被落下的「落下的東西」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.31,0:19:07.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}算了 隨便敷衍一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.05,0:19:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哦？是海嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.04,0:19:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.06,0:19:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}難道你也…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.64,0:19:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}找到了嗎？落下的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.74,0:19:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}有澤同學…你怎麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.08,0:19:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這個嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.46,0:19:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}還用問嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.26,0:19:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我要是真的還喜歡小海的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.93,0:19:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼…這麼突然
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.49,0:19:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}和什麼時候說沒關係的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.18,0:19:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}昨晚你說過你還沒有喜歡的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.16,0:19:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.05,0:19:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我只是說沒有女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.66,0:19:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喜歡的人 是有的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.62,0:19:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我是說真的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.22,0:20:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.12,0:20:11.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你這是怎麼了？有澤同學
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.00,0:20:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我挺任性的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.13,0:20:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這樣…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.46,0:20:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我已經忍不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.17,0:20:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}而且我是肉食系的！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.31,0:20:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}等 等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.69,0:20:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}力氣意外的大…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.10,0:20:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在女孩子面前…還要什麼節操呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.53,0:20:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.13,0:20:46.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}到底去哪兒了啊 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.29,0:20:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}雖然我不自覺的就來找他們了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.11,0:20:55.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但就算是找到了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.11,0:20:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我…又該如何呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.71,0:21:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.59,0:21:12.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}美…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.01,0:21:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}小海
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.27,0:21:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}樹…下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.76,0:21:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}學…姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.53,0:21:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誰也…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.88,0:21:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒回來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.65,0:23:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}{\blur5}告訴我嘛…檸檬
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.23,0:23:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}{\blur5}海人的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.11,0:23:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}{\blur5}他肯定是在想些什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.38,0:23:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}{\blur5}您真是明察秋毫！
